Anglo Platinum Ltd. (AMS)  and  Impala
Platinum Holdings Ltd. (IMP) , the worldâ€™s largest miners of the
precious metal, are in talks with Zimbabwe about selling
majority stakes in their local operations, Reuters said, citing
